summary:
Random observation. 
 Tony Stark (MCU) = Bruce Wayne + Hal Jordan  Supporting evidence:   He’s crazy brilliant in a multitude of...
body:
Random observation.

Tony Stark (MCU) = Bruce Wayne + Hal Jordan

Supporting evidence:

He’s crazy brilliant in a multitude of areas. He’s also a hot mess, and everybody knows it. 

He’ll throw himself into a sketchy space portal and figure out how not to die on the way back. He’ll also learn thermonuclear astrophysics overnight and follow a lead down a million rabbit holes without flinching.

He’s completely irreverent and unintimidated by power/authority/anything but his own conscience.

Which holds him to higher standards than anyone else ever could.

Both of which are traits shared by Bruce and Hal.

Conclusion: The similarities become a little uncanny the more I stare at it.

summary: (I just wanted to write something) (has angst) (and death of main character) (sorry, btw) They are trapped. There was no escape....
body:
(I just wanted to write something) (has angst) (and death of main character) (sorry, btw)

They are trapped.

There was no escape.

They were going to die.

At least Peter was safe and that made the idea of ​​dying less painful. The world is a painful place. Painful and unfair. Soon as he and Stephen were beginning their life together, death would separate them.

He does not want to die.

Not now.

He wanted to die old and tired, lying in bed in the arms of his love and that his last feeling was simply love, love and love.

But now this future is impossible.

Tears shine in her eyes, fear and sadness make her body shudder. A trembling hand caresses his face with affection, Whiskey eyes look into the blue eyes.

He swallows the dry.

He does not want to die.

Not now.

“Don’t cry.” Your voice is sweet and warm. “Just look at me. Ignore the world and look at me.” Stephen asks gently and he nods.

Your love gathers your foreheads gently and time runs out quickly. They do not have enough time to say how much they love each other and there may not be enough words to describe the feeling.

“I don’t want to die now.”

“I know.” A lonely tear trickles down his face. “I don’t want too.”

The time is over.

(I hope you have cried as much as I did) (My english sucks, sorry)

summary: So... I decided to make my own Starker Mafia AU™ Peter is a gang leader and he still got his spider powers, but he never became...
caption:
So… I decided to make my own Starker Mafia AU™

Peter is a gang leader and he still got his spider powers, but he never became Spider-man. He lost both Ben and May when he was 15 and after he avenged their death, he dropped out of high school and became a gangster.

Tony is an engineer who develops weapons and technology for S.H.I.E.L.D. and he’s also the boss of the biggest mafia in the country. Iron Man doesn’t exist in this AU, but the Avengers do, he’s not part of them.

I’m gonna be drawing more about this AU in the future ❤️
